      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example retains its crisp mechanical throttle response and high-revving character. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis' known stress points. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing high-quality bushings for telepathic feedback. While the aesthetic reflects its use as a spirited driver, the drivetrain is robust, exhibiting linear power delivery and the signature metallic rasp of the M-tuned exhaust. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a mechanically sound platform without the 'museum piece' premium.",
